data.description: Highly Sought after neighborhood!  This single story home is a RARE Find...This home Has it ALL!  Formal Living & Dining, Family room, Split 4 bedroom and HUGE DEN! Newer Wood/tile in all the right spots.. Newer carpet in bedrooms, Ceiling fans, HUGE Open Kitchen with ALL SS appliances included, Oversized Laundry room w/ folding area AND Newer Washer and Dryer!  The best part...Home is placed on over sized lot with Huge Pool!  Beautiful water/ Fire features!  A must See!  This is going to go Quick!
